Package: BlastCuratoR
Title: Curation of Taxonomic Annotations from BLAST Results
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Valeria", "Flores Almaraz", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "valeria.stephany.flores.almaraz@ut.ee"),
    person("Vladimir", "Mikyrukov", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "vladimir.mikyrukov@gmail.com")
Description: When running BLAST against a reference database, each query often returns multiple hits that vary in percent identity, E-value, bitscore, and other metrics. Directly adopting the top hitâ€™s species-level assignment can lead to overconfident or erroneous annotations. `BlastCuratoR` applies a set of rules and confidence thresholds to perform automated curation of the taxonomy annotation results.
